casebody.data:
John E. WINFIELD, petitioner,
v.
TROY STEEL, Warden. No. 13-10341 (13A1194). Supreme Court of the United States June 17, 2014.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO

*2838and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Missouri denied.
